===Noun===
'''[[lateral]] [[line]]'''
# a [[sense]] [[organ]] of a [[fish]] running [[lengthwise]] down each of its sides from the vicinity of the [[operculum]] to the base of the tail, used to detect [[movement]] and [[vibration]] in the surrounding water.

